    The final temperature for this step scales linearly with volume: $T_2 = 2 T_1 = 600 " K"$.
    
  - *Step 2 (Isothermal compression):* $W_23 = -n R T_2 ln(V_1 / V_2) = -2 times 8.314 times 600 times ln(0.5) = +6915.4 " J"$
    
